{
  "chapter": 3,
  "chapter_summary": "第三回「第一神剑」场景转至小镇太白居酒铺。一个穷困潦倒的八尺大汉（燕南天乔装）以一口锈剑戏弄镖师雷老大，先以小技巧让锈剑削断精钢剑，再以一千两银子将「宝剑」卖给雷老大等人。总镖头沈轻虹到来后识破真相，原来那穷汉正是当今江湖第一神剑燕南天。燕南天的书童江琴现身，告知江枫遣散家仆、秘密出逃之事。沈轻虹恳求燕南天相助应对十二星相劫镖，但燕南天心系二弟安危，拒绝黄金酬谢，带上江琴急赴与江枫会合。",
  "dialogues": [
    {
      "speaker": "char_lei_lao_da",
      "speaker_name": "雷老大",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "太白居！这破屋子、烂摊子也可叫作太白居么？",
      "tone": "大笑",
      "chapter": 3
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_qian_er",
      "speaker_name": "钱二",
      "listener": "char_lei_lao_da",
      "text": "雷老大，你可错了，李太白的几首诗虽写得蛮不错，但却也是个没钱没势的穷小子，住在这种地方正合适。",
      "tone": "笑",
      "chapter": 3
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_yan_nan_tian",
      "speaker_name": "穷汉",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "臭不可闻，俗不可耐……",
      "tone": "喃喃",
      "chapter": 3
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_yan_nan_tian",
      "speaker_name": "穷汉",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "快拿酒来，解解俗气。",
      "tone": "大喝",
      "chapter": 3
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_sun_lao_san",
      "speaker_name": "孙老三",
      "listener": "char_lei_lao_da",
      "text": "总镖头就要来了，咱们何必多事？",
      "tone": "低声道",
      "chapter": 3
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lei_lao_da",
      "speaker_name": "雷老大",
      "listener": "char_sun_lao_san",
      "text": "孙老三，老总说的可是这地方？你听错没有？",
      "tone": "道",
      "chapter": 3
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_qian_er",
      "speaker_name": "钱二",
      "listener": "char_lei_lao_da",
      "text": "不错！就是这儿，老总这次来，听说要来见一位大英雄，所以要咱们先将礼物带来，在这里等着。",
      "tone": "截口笑",
      "chapter": 3
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_yan_nan_tian",
      "speaker_name": "穷汉",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "世上哪有那样的人，那样的剑！",
      "tone": "放声大笑",
      "chapter": 3
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lei_lao_da",
      "speaker_name": "雷老大",
      "listener": "char_yan_nan_tian",
      "text": "是谁在这里胡说八道？快给我滚过来！",
      "tone": "拍桌怒吼",
      "chapter": 3
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_qian_er",
      "speaker_name": "钱二",
      "listener": "char_yan_nan_tian",
      "text": "看来朋友你也是练剑的，所以听人说话，就难免有些不服气，但朋友可知道咱们说的是谁么？",
      "tone": "笑",
      "chapter": 3
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_yan_nan_tian",
      "speaker_name": "穷汉",
      "listener": "char_qian_er",
      "text": "谁？",
      "tone": "懒洋洋",
      "chapter": 3
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_qian_er",
      "speaker_name": "钱二",
      "listener": "char_yan_nan_tian",
      "text": "燕大侠，燕南天，燕神剑，哈哈，朋友你若真的是练剑的，听到这名字，就总该服气了吧！",
      "tone": "笑",
      "chapter": 3
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_yan_nan_tian",
      "speaker_name": "穷汉",
      "listener": "char_qian_er",
      "text": "燕南天？燕南天是谁？",
      "tone": "嘻嘻笑",
      "chapter": 3
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lei_lao_da",
      "speaker_name": "雷老大",
      "listener": "char_yan_nan_tian",
      "text": "咱们纵不认得他，但却也知道他长得远比你这厮帅得多了，他那柄剑更不知要比你这口强胜千百倍。",
      "tone": "拍桌吼",
      "chapter": 3
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_yan_nan_tian",
      "speaker_name": "穷汉",
      "listener": "char_lei_lao_da",
      "text": "某家这口剑，正是削铁如泥的利器。",
      "tone": "道",
      "chapter": 3
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_yan_nan_tian",
      "speaker_name": "穷汉",
      "listener": "char_lei_lao_da",
      "text": "好，抽出你的剑来试试！",
      "tone": "霍然长身",
      "chapter": 3
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_yan_nan_tian",
      "speaker_name": "穷汉",
      "listener": "char_lei_lao_da",
      "text": "如何？",
      "tone": "哈哈大笑",
      "chapter": 3
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lei_lao_da",
      "speaker_name": "雷老大",
      "listener": "char_yan_nan_tian",
      "text": "好……好剑，果然好剑。",
      "tone": "张口结舌",
      "chapter": 3
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_yan_nan_tian",
      "speaker_name": "穷汉",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "如此好剑，只可惜在我手里糟蹋了。",
      "tone": "长叹",
      "chapter": 3
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lei_lao_da",
      "speaker_name": "雷老大",
      "listener": "char_yan_nan_tian",
      "text": "不……不知朋友可……可有意出让？",
      "tone": "眼睛亮",
      "chapter": 3
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_yan_nan_tian",
      "speaker_name": "穷汉",
      "listener": "char_lei_lao_da",
      "text": "虽然有意，怎奈难遇买主。",
      "tone": "道",
      "chapter": 3
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lei_lao_da",
      "speaker_name": "雷老大",
      "listener": "char_yan_nan_tian",
      "text": "我……我这买主，你看如何？",
      "tone": "大喜",
      "chapter": 3
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_yan_nan_tian",
      "speaker_name": "穷汉",
      "listener": "char_lei_lao_da",
      "text": "看你也有些英雄气概，也可配得上这口宝剑了，只是……你眼力既差，却不知出手如何？",
      "tone": "颔首",
      "chapter": 3
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_yan_nan_tian",
      "speaker_name": "穷汉",
      "listener": "char_lei_lao_da",
      "text": "此剑本是无价之宝，但常言说的好，红粉赠佳人，宝剑赠英雄……好，一千两卖给你也罢。",
      "tone": "沉吟",
      "chapter": 3
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_yan_nan_tian",
      "speaker_name": "穷汉",
      "listener": "char_lei_lao_da",
      "text": "不用点了，错不了的……那，剑在这里，神兵利器，惟有德者佩之，你以后可要小心谦虚，否则这种神兵利器怕也会变顽铁……",
      "tone": "笑",
      "chapter": 3
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_yan_nan_tian",
      "speaker_name": "穷汉",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "某家去了，这里的酒账，全算我的。",
      "tone": "笑",
      "chapter": 3
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_qian_er",
      "speaker_name": "钱二",
      "listener": "char_lei_lao_da",
      "text": "咱们雷老大得了这口剑，可当真是如虎添翼了。日后这江湖，还怕不是咱们雷老大的天下？",
      "tone": "笑",
      "chapter": 3
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_shen_qing_hong",
      "speaker_name": "沈总镖头",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "真的么？那可当真是可喜可贺之事。",
      "tone": "笑",
      "chapter": 3
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_shen_qing_hong",
      "speaker_name": "沈总镖头",
      "listener": "char_lei_lao_da",
      "text": "不瞒各位，如此利器，我倒真是从未见过，不知雷兄可能让我开开眼界。",
      "tone": "微笑",
      "chapter": 3
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_shen_qing_hong",
      "speaker_name": "沈总镖头",
      "l": null,
      "text": "雷兄小心了。",
      "tone": "微笑",
      "chapter": 3
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_shen_qing_hong",
      "speaker_name": "沈总镖头",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "这也算是宝剑么？",
      "tone": "冷笑",
      "chapter": 3
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_shen_qing_hong",
      "speaker_name": "沈总镖头",
      "listener": "char_lei_lao_da",
      "text": "方才明明是你上了别人的当了。",
      "tone": "冷冷",
      "chapter": 3
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_shen_qing_hong",
      "speaker_name": "沈总镖头",
      "listener": "char_lei_lao_da",
      "text": "那人双眉可是特别浓重？骨骼可是特别大？一双眼睛平时永远半张半闭，仿佛有好几天未睡觉的模样？",
      "tone": "变色",
      "chapter": 3
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_shen_qing_hong",
      "speaker_name": "沈总镖头",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "只叹你们随我多年，不想竟还都是有眼无珠的瞎子。",
      "tone": "仰天长叹",
      "chapter": 3
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_shen_qing_hong",
      "speaker_name": "沈总镖头",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "他便是当今江湖第一神剑，燕南天，也就是我此番专程来拜见的人。",
      "tone": "一字字缓缓",
      "chapter": 3
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_jiang_qin",
      "speaker_name": "江琴",
      "listener": "char_yan_nan_tian",
      "text": "是燕大爷么？",
      "tone": "悄声",
      "chapter": 3
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_yan_nan_tian",
      "speaker_name": "燕南天",
      "listener": "char_jiang_qin",
      "text": "你可是我江二弟差来的？",
      "tone": "沉声",
      "chapter": 3
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_jiang_qin",
      "speaker_name": "江琴",
      "listener": "char_yan_nan_tian",
      "text": "小人正是江二爷的书童江琴。",
      "tone": "道",
      "chapter": 3
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_yan_nan_tian",
      "speaker_name": "燕南天",
      "listener": "char_jiang_qin",
      "text": "你怎地此时才来？",
      "tone": "厉声",
      "chapter": 3
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_jiang_qin",
      "speaker_name": "江琴",
      "listener": "char_yan_nan_tian",
      "text": "小人……小人怕行踪落在别人眼里，是以只敢在夜间行事，而……而小人虽从小跟着公子，轻身功夫却可怜得很。",
      "tone": "垂手",
      "chapter": 3
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_yan_nan_tian",
      "speaker_name": "燕南天",
      "listener": "char_jiang_qin",
      "text": "你家公子令人送来书信，要我在此相候，信中却不说明原因，便知其中必有极大的隐密……这究竟是什么事？",
      "tone": "缓缓",
      "chapter": 3
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_jiang_qin",
      "speaker_name": "江琴",
      "listener": "char_yan_nan_tian",
      "text": "我家公子不知为了什么，突然将家人全都遣散了，只留下小人，然后又令小人到这里来见大爷，请大爷由这条废道上去接他。看情形……我家公子似乎在躲避着什么强仇大敌。",
      "tone": "躬身",
      "chapter": 3
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_yan_nan_tian",
      "speaker_name": "燕南天",
      "listener": "char_jiang_qin",
      "text": "哦？有这等事！他为何不早说？……唉，二弟做事总是如此糊涂，纵是强仇大敌，我兄弟难道还怕了他们？",
      "tone": "动容",
      "chapter": 3
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_shen_qing_hong",
      "speaker_name": "沈轻虹",
      "listener": "char_yan_nan_tian",
      "text": "燕大侠……燕大侠……",
      "tone": "大呼",
      "chapter": 3
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_yan_nan_tian",
      "speaker_name": "燕南天",
      "listener": "char_shen_qing_hong",
      "text": "来的可是威远、镇远、宁远三大镖局的总镖头，江湖人称「飞花满天，落地无声」的沈轻虹么？",
      "tone": "沉声",
      "chapter": 3
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_shen_qing_hong",
      "speaker_name": "沈轻虹",
      "listener": "char_yan_nan_tian",
      "text": "不敢，正是小人……弟子们有眼无珠，不认得燕大侠……",
      "tone": "躬身拜",
      "chapter": 3
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_yan_nan_tian",
      "speaker_name": "燕南天",
      "listener": "char_shen_qing_hong",
      "text": "我听得他们竟敢说要请诗仙喝酒，便觉有气，但瞧在你家镖主面上，也不能揍他们一顿，若不取他们几文银子，怎出得了气！",
      "tone": "大笑",
      "chapter": 3
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_yan_nan_tian",
      "speaker_name": "燕南天",
      "listener": "char_shen_qing_hong",
      "text": "你可是来寻我的？",
      "tone": "笑声突顿",
      "chapter": 3
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_shen_qing_hong",
      "speaker_name": "沈轻虹",
      "listener": "char_yan_nan_tian",
      "text": "晚辈正是专程前来拜见燕大侠。",
      "tone": "道",
      "chapter": 3
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_yan_nan_tian",
      "speaker_name": "燕南天",
      "listener": "char_shen_qing_hong",
      "text": "你怎知我在这里？",
      "tone": "厉声",
      "chapter": 3
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_shen_qing_hong",
      "speaker_name": "沈轻虹",
      "listener": "char_yan_nan_tian",
      "text": "晚辈正值走投无路，幸得一位前辈的指点，说是燕大侠这两天必在此间等人，是以晚辈才赶来。",
      "tone": "道",
      "chapter": 3
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_yan_nan_tian",
      "speaker_name": "燕南天",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "原来又是那醉鬼多口……",
      "tone": "展颜笑",
      "chapter": 3
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_yan_nan_tian",
      "speaker_name": "燕南天",
      "listener": "char_shen_qing_hong",
      "text": "你如此捧我，想必有求于我。",
      "tone": "笑",
      "chapter": 3
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_shen_qing_hong",
      "speaker_name": "沈轻虹",
      "listener": "char_yan_nan_tian",
      "text": "不瞒前辈，晚辈接着一票红货，价值可说无法估计，此事本做得十分隐密，哪知不知怎地，这风声竟走漏到「十二星相」的耳里，竟令人送来「星辰帖」，明言劫镖，晚辈自然不敢再走镖上路……",
      "tone": "叹",
      "chapter": 3
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_yan_nan_tian",
      "speaker_name": "燕南天",
      "listener": "char_shen_qing_hong",
      "text": "你莫非是要我来为你保镖不成？",
      "tone": "道",
      "chapter": 3
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_shen_qing_hong",
      "speaker_name": "沈轻虹",
      "listener": "char_yan_nan_tian",
      "text": "晚辈不敢……晚辈知道前辈在此，是以已将「十二星相」约在附近，只求前辈抽空一行，只要前辈吩咐两句，「十二星相」纵有天大的胆子，想必也再不敢来打这票红货的主意。",
      "tone": "道",
      "chapter": 3
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_yan_nan_tian",
      "speaker_name": "燕南天",
      "listener": "char_shen_qing_hong",
      "text": "你既无力护镖，为何又要接下？",
      "tone": "沉声",
      "chapter": 3
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_yan_nan_tian",
      "speaker_name": "燕南天",
      "listener": "char_shen_qing_hong",
      "text": "十二星相恶名久著，若非他们行踪委实隐密，我早已将之除去，此事我本非不愿出手助你……",
      "tone": "道",
      "chapter": 3
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_yan_nan_tian",
      "speaker_name": "燕南天",
      "listener": "char_shen_qing_hong",
      "text": "你莫谢我，我虽有心助你，怎奈我此刻却另有急事，那是片刻也延误不得的。",
      "tone": "沉声",
      "chapter": 3
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_yan_nan_tian",
      "speaker_name": "燕南天",
      "listener": "char_shen_qing_hong",
      "text": "沈轻虹，你纵将天下所有的黄金都送到我面前，也不能将我与二弟相见的时候耽误片刻……",
      "tone": "仰天狂笑",
      "chapter": 3
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_yan_nan_tian",
      "speaker_name": "燕南天",
      "listener": "char_jiang_qin",
      "text": "我先去了，你跟着来！",
      "tone": "喝",
      "chapter": 3
    }
  ],
